>> source: Magnolia
>> serves: 2 cups

Combine 2 cups @small broccoli florets{2%cups}; 1 cup packed fresh @basil{1%cup}; 1 cup shredded @Parmesan{1%cup} cheese; 2/3 cup @toasted pine nuts{2/3%cup}; 2/3 cup extra virgin @olive oil{2/3%cup}; 3 cloves @garlic{3%cloves}, halved; 1 tsp kosher @salt{1%tsp} in a #food processor{}.

Process until nearly smooth. Add up to 2 Tbsp additional olive oil to reach desired consistency.
